      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical work and cosmetic restoration. The engine currently struggles to start and has a noticeable knock, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. Externally, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling across most surfaces. The interior is in rough shape with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics, making this an ideal project car or parts donor for someone with the right tools and time.",
