      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Alpine White. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to produce a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to an M-Variable limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with treated shells, and a full rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis dynamics are as sharp as the day it left Regensburg. No pixel degradation in the dash, flawless Nappa leather, and original factory paint throughout.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
