    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded entirely from the elements. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish without a single stone chip or swirl mark, while the interior remains a sanctuary of untouched premium leather and factory-fresh carpeting. Every stitch is perfect, and the cabin still retains that unmistakable new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014whisper-quiet, incredibly responsive, and accompanied by a comprehensive service history that documents a lifetime of preventative care. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless, turn-key masterpiece that satisfies even the most rigorous inspection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
